data.description:
Welcome to this charming 3-bd, 2-bath house in a thriving up-and-coming area! This well-maintained home offers a spacious and inviting open concept design that's perfect for modern living.

As you step inside, you'll notice the neutral color walls that create a soothing and versatile backdrop for your personal style and decor. The living area seamlessly flows into the dining and kitchen spaces, making it ideal for gatherings with family and friends.

The updated yard features a lush grassy section with pavers and a covered patio, perfect for relaxation and entertainment. The RV gate and side parking offer convenient storage options for your outdoor toys and vehicles.

Easy access to the 303, you will also enjoy the convenience of shopping centers, restaurants, and entertainment.
